/- Number field `K(α)` with with α root of polynomial `X^5 + 10*X^3 - 40*X^2 - 15*X - 232`.
Class number `5`, generated by class of ideal `J = (2, 1/4*a^4 + 7/4*a^2 - 15/2*a - 5)`. We have `J ^ 5 = (α)`. -/

/- Ring of integers with basis `[1, a, a^2, 1/4*a^3 - 1/2*a^2 - 1/4*a, 1/4*a^4 - 1/4*a^2 - 1/2*a]` -/

